1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,310
<font size="36" color="#070508"><b>{\an5}m 0 0 l 0 102 32 102 b 3 75 3 32 32 0</b></font>

2
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,310
<font size="36" color="#070508"><b>{\an5}<font face="Georgia">OSHI <font color="#cb0085">NO <font color="#070508">KO</font></font></font></b></font>

3
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,310
<font size="36" color="#070508"><b>{\an5}m 0 0 l 0 102 32 102 b 3 75 3 32 32 0</b></font>

4
00:01:31,820 --> 00:01:36,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>If a film creator like me wants to show 
a movie on cinema screens nationwide,</i></font>

5
00:01:36,100 --> 00:01:38,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>there are several steps 
one needs to go through.</i></font>

6
00:01:39,870 --> 00:01:43,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Step 1: Get a movie producer to help.</i></font>

7
00:01:43,330 --> 00:01:46,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, time to go scrounge up some money.</font>

8
00:01:45,710 --> 00:01:50,460
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="12"><font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#252525">Pitch
The 15-Year Lie</font></font></font></b></font>

9
00:01:46,200 --> 00:01:48,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I polished the pitch myself.</font>

10
00:01:48,870 --> 00:01:51,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All you need to do is express 
your passion for the project.</font>

11
00:01:52,840 --> 00:01:55,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Step 2: Gather investors.</i></font>

12
00:01:55,680 --> 00:02:00,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>A movie takes around two to three 
hundred million yen to make.</i></font>

13
00:02:00,640 --> 00:02:04,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>You get a bunch of companies 
to front these production costs,</i></font>

14
00:02:04,170 --> 00:02:06,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>promising them rights 
and profits in return.</i></font>

15
00:02:06,880 --> 00:02:09,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's what you call 
production by committee.</i></font>

16
00:02:10,320 --> 00:02:13,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Step 3: Make your pitch to distributors.</i></font>

17
00:02:14,140 --> 00:02:17,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Your distributor's reach will determine 
how many screens your movie can secure.</i></font>

18
00:02:18,310 --> 00:02:20,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>If you want your film to go big,</i></font>

19
00:02:20,620 --> 00:02:24,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>you get the most powerful 
distributor you can, but...</i></font>

20
00:02:24,940 --> 00:02:27,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Damn it. All the big names said no.</font>

21
00:02:27,630 --> 00:02:31,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, it is based on a delicate subject. 
Major players tend to avoid that.</font>

22
00:02:32,420 --> 00:02:36,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But some distributors 
do like risky projects like this one,</font>

23
00:02:36,500 --> 00:02:37,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so let's be patient.</font>

24
00:02:40,070 --> 00:02:42,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't worry. We should get a bite soon.</font>

25
00:02:43,390 --> 00:02:45,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Kaburagi's a freelance producer.</i></font>

26
00:02:45,940 --> 00:02:50,690
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="20"><font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#4f433e">Pitch</font></font></font></b></font>

27
00:02:45,940 --> 00:02:50,690
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#16131f">The 15-Year Lie</font></font></b></font>

28
00:02:45,940 --> 00:02:50,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He doesn't work for any one distributor, 
so he has to go around pitching projects.</i></font>

29
00:02:50,690 --> 00:02:55,150
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="24"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><font color="#080307">Distributor A</font></font></font></b></font>

30
00:02:51,060 --> 00:02:54,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>On the plus side, that means 
he can try every distributor out there.</i></font>

31
00:02:51,480 --> 00:02:55,150
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font face="Arial"><font color="#080307">Distributor B</font></font></b></font>

32
00:02:52,230 --> 00:02:55,150
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="19"><font face="Verdana"><font color="#080307">Distributor C</font></font></font></b></font>

33
00:02:52,990 --> 00:02:55,150
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="21"><font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#080307">Distributor D</font></font></font></b></font>

34
00:02:55,570 --> 00:03:00,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}When you're hellbent on releasing a film, 
a man like him becomes real dependable.</i></font>

35
00:02:59,120 --> 00:03:02,080
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="30"><font color="#3d353e">Eikyo Headquarters Building II</font></font></b></font>

36
00:02:59,120 --> 00:03:02,080
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="12"><font color="#3d353e">Members of the Board</font></font></b></font>

37
00:02:59,120 --> 00:03:02,080
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="12"><font color="#3d353e">Planning Department</font></font></b></font>

38
00:02:59,120 --> 00:03:02,080
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="12"><font color="#3d353e">Sales Department</font></font></b></font>

39
00:02:59,120 --> 00:03:02,080
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="12"><font color="#746964">Production Department III</font></font></b></font>

40
00:02:59,120 --> 00:03:02,080
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="12"><font color="#746964">Conference Rooms II</font></font></b></font>

41
00:02:59,120 --> 00:03:02,080
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="12"><font color="#746964">Production Department II</font></font></b></font>

42
00:03:00,370 --> 00:03:02,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}The next one's our main target.</font>

43
00:03:10,340 --> 00:03:14,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ugh. Everything takes money, money, money.</font>

44
00:03:16,140 --> 00:03:18,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Would you have preferred 
to make an independent film?</font>

45
00:03:18,420 --> 00:03:20,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not saying that, but man.</font>

46
00:03:21,470 --> 00:03:22,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Say...</font>

47
00:03:22,780 --> 00:03:29,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nowadays, anyone with a smartphone 
can make films and release them online.</font>

48
00:03:29,020 --> 00:03:31,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What reason do any of us 
have to stick to theatrical releases?</font>

49
00:03:32,020 --> 00:03:33,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's an easy one.</font>

50
00:03:33,620 --> 00:03:37,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because that's the only way you can 
become the center of a movement.</font>

51
00:03:38,460 --> 00:03:42,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can only kick off a movement 
big enough to be a social phenomenon</font>

52
00:03:42,110 --> 00:03:45,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">with content fueled 
by massive amounts of money.</font>

53
00:03:45,570 --> 00:03:47,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A social phenomenon, eh?</font>

54
00:03:47,580 --> 00:03:51,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I never expected the humble Director 
Gotanda to have such lofty ambitions.</font>

55
00:03:51,900 --> 00:03:57,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please. Every creator wants their work 
appreciated by more people for longer—</font>

56
00:03:57,580 --> 00:04:01,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">to be something that is 
celebrated a century from now.</font>

57
00:04:01,060 --> 00:04:02,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're such an artist.</font>

58
00:04:03,430 --> 00:04:05,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What can people even say 
a century from now?</font>

59
00:04:05,590 --> 00:04:10,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Backhanded compliments like, 
"Wow, it actually holds up"? Spare me.</font>

60
00:04:11,270 --> 00:04:14,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In my eyes, as long as it 
makes money, anything goes.</font>

61
00:04:14,820 --> 00:04:16,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You greedy money-grubber.</font>

62
00:04:18,450 --> 00:04:21,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Anyway, our work's not done yet.</font>

63
00:04:21,410 --> 00:04:23,870
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="18"><font color="#322d2f">Villain</font></font></b></font>

64
00:04:21,410 --> 00:04:23,870
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="15"><font color="#322d2f">Aqua Hoshino</font></font></b></font>

65
00:04:21,410 --> 00:04:23,870
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="14"><font color="#322d2f">Confirmed</font></font></b></font>

66
00:04:21,410 --> 00:04:23,870
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="18"><font color="#322d2f">Agency President Candidates</font></font></b></font>

67
00:04:21,410 --> 00:04:23,870
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="15"><font color="#322d2f">Melt Narushima


Masato Murakami


Yuu Miyashita</font></font></b></font>

68
00:04:21,410 --> 00:04:23,870
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="14"><font color="#322d2f">Opening in Schedule


Negotiating w/ Agency


Opening in Schedule</font></font></b></font>

69
00:04:21,410 --> 00:04:23,870
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="18"><font color="#322d2f">Theater Actor Candidates</font></font></b></font>

70
00:04:21,410 --> 00:04:23,870
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="15"><font color="#322d2f">Takashi Ichikawa</font></font></b></font>

71
00:04:21,410 --> 00:04:23,870
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="14"><font color="#322d2f">Opening in Schedule</font></font></b></font>

72
00:04:21,800 --> 00:04:23,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Step 4: Casting.</i></font>

73
00:04:24,220 --> 00:04:27,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The main lead can make a difference of 
hundreds of millions in the box office.</font>

74
00:04:27,960 --> 00:04:31,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lots of projects live or die 
by who they're able to cast.</font>

75
00:04:31,500 --> 00:04:35,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But popular actors don't often 
have much room in their schedules,</font>

76
00:04:35,710 --> 00:04:37,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and they can be picky, too.</font>

77
00:04:37,760 --> 00:04:41,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I had an actress earmarked 
for the lead role, but she's out.</font>

78
00:04:41,670 --> 00:04:43,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Something go wrong?</font>

79
00:04:43,450 --> 00:04:48,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She got pulled at the last second. 
I've heard rumors that she's MIA.</font>

80
00:04:49,080 --> 00:04:51,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wonder what happened.</font>

81
00:04:52,210 --> 00:04:57,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Either way, among all the talent 
I took under my wing and sent jobs to,</font>

82
00:04:57,180 --> 00:05:00,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I picked out the biggest names right now 
to fill out our prospective cast.</font>

83
00:05:00,840 --> 00:05:03,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Times like these are 
why I did them all those favors.</font>

84
00:05:03,790 --> 00:05:05,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's the culmination of all my work.</font>

85
00:05:06,450 --> 00:05:11,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now, how many of them 
will repay those favors?</font>

86
00:05:12,020 --> 00:05:15,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He constantly networks 
with actors and investors,</i></font>

87
00:05:15,260 --> 00:05:18,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>knows all the ins and outs of filmmaking,</i></font>

88
00:05:19,010 --> 00:05:21,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and oversees and runs entire productions.</i></font>

89
00:05:21,930 --> 00:05:24,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He does it all without breaking 
a sweat, but it's really not easy.</i></font>

90
00:05:25,470 --> 00:05:28,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He might only ever talk about money,</i></font>

91
00:05:28,900 --> 00:05:31,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>but nothing he does 
could be done without passion.</i></font>

92
00:05:32,790 --> 00:05:34,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Director Gotanda.</font>

93
00:05:34,810 --> 00:05:39,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm genuinely expecting a movie 
capable of sparking a social phenomenon.</font>

94
00:05:40,380 --> 00:05:41,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If it does that,</font>

95
00:05:41,880 --> 00:05:43,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll make out like a bandit.</font>

96
00:05:45,870 --> 00:05:47,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Damn greedy money-grubber.</font>

97
00:05:45,870 --> 00:05:48,330
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="12"><font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#252525">Pitch
The 15-Year Lie</font></font></font></b></font>

98
00:05:49,230 --> 00:05:50,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The ultimate choice!</font>

99
00:05:51,380 --> 00:05:52,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Option one:</font>

100
00:05:52,250 --> 00:05:55,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Get dropped into a pit full of tarantulas!</font>

101
00:05:55,210 --> 00:05:58,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Option two: Get shot up by a machine gun!</font>

102
00:05:58,590 --> 00:06:02,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Option three: Get flattened 
by a falling meteorite!</font>

103
00:06:03,180 --> 00:06:05,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Which would you pick out of those?</font>

104
00:06:05,140 --> 00:06:06,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where did this even come from?</font>

105
00:06:06,710 --> 00:06:09,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just answer me.</font>

106
00:06:09,200 --> 00:06:10,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, option three. The meteorite.</font>

107
00:06:11,290 --> 00:06:13,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">At least I'd die before I felt any pain.</font>

108
00:06:15,120 --> 00:06:18,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Bzzt! You're a moron if you choose 
anything other than option one!</font>

109
00:06:18,920 --> 00:06:22,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tarantula bites can hurt, 
but they're not venomous!</font>

110
00:06:22,830 --> 00:06:24,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've got shit for brains, Aqua!</font>

111
00:06:24,150 --> 00:06:25,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Yeah, I get it.</font>

112
00:06:24,920 --> 00:06:26,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, you've got a shit personality.</font>

113
00:06:25,440 --> 00:06:26,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}I know, right?</font>

114
00:06:26,960 --> 00:06:27,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Aqua?</font>

115
00:06:28,330 --> 00:06:30,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}As in, Aqua Hoshino?</font>

116
00:06:30,700 --> 00:06:33,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yikes! Let's scram!</font>

117
00:06:31,640 --> 00:06:33,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Is that really him?</font>

118
00:06:34,100 --> 00:06:36,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Somebody's famous now.</font>

119
00:06:36,790 --> 00:06:41,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll have to think twice before even 
saying your name in public.</font>

120
00:06:41,670 --> 00:06:44,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, especially after that story broke.</font>

121
00:06:44,920 --> 00:06:49,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just goes to show that Ai's murder 
left a lasting impression on people.</font>

122
00:06:51,790 --> 00:06:53,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is a problem, though.</font>

123
00:06:53,560 --> 00:06:55,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What am I supposed to call you 
when we're out?</font>

124
00:06:57,120 --> 00:06:58,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ah-kun.</font>

125
00:06:59,730 --> 00:07:02,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That should be safe 
to say out in public, right?</font>

126
00:07:03,180 --> 00:07:06,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? I'm suggesting it 
for your peace of mind.</font>

127
00:07:06,680 --> 00:07:11,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're only here because you protected me, 
so I'll help you out however I can.</font>

128
00:07:12,240 --> 00:07:16,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But don't get the wrong idea! I'm not 
trying to act like your girlfriend here.</font>

129
00:07:17,340 --> 00:07:20,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see you as a dear friend, nothing more.</font>

130
00:07:20,700 --> 00:07:22,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh...</font>

131
00:07:22,040 --> 00:07:24,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd never look at you romantically!</font>

132
00:07:24,470 --> 00:07:27,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Besides, you have a girlfriend and all.</font>

133
00:07:27,090 --> 00:07:28,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I broke up with Akane, but okay.</font>

134
00:07:31,160 --> 00:07:32,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hmm? Wha?</font>

135
00:07:33,650 --> 00:07:35,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, okay...</font>

136
00:07:35,540 --> 00:07:37,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You and Akane Kurokawa split...</font>

137
00:07:38,560 --> 00:07:40,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Me and my big mouth!</i></font>

138
00:07:40,900 --> 00:07:44,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I just had to go and ruin my big chance!</i></font>

139
00:07:45,030 --> 00:07:46,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So call me whatever you like.</font>

140
00:07:47,240 --> 00:07:48,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

141
00:07:51,690 --> 00:07:54,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, I've got a recording to get to.</font>

142
00:07:54,910 --> 00:07:56,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Bye, Ah-kun.</font>

143
00:07:56,450 --> 00:07:57,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just get going.</font>

144
00:07:58,540 --> 00:08:00,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ah-kun, Ah-kun!</font>

145
00:08:02,180 --> 00:08:03,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Heh, heh, heh.</font>

146
00:08:03,710 --> 00:08:06,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now, isn't that something?</font>

147
00:08:06,020 --> 00:08:10,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"Ah-kun," she said. 
You two have grown awfully close.</font>

148
00:08:10,350 --> 00:08:11,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kinda.</font>

149
00:08:11,510 --> 00:08:15,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kana-chan's been in good spirits lately.</font>

150
00:08:15,300 --> 00:08:19,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I love to see it, personally speaking.</font>

151
00:08:19,290 --> 00:08:21,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But, well, you know...</font>

152
00:08:21,930 --> 00:08:27,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I heard from Akane that you two broke up, 
but this is leaving me very conflicted.</font>

153
00:08:27,220 --> 00:08:32,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It'd help your dear MEMcho out 
a bunch if you handled this tactfully.</font>

154
00:08:32,510 --> 00:08:34,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've got nothing to worry about.</font>

155
00:08:35,320 --> 00:08:36,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm done with all that.</font>

156
00:08:37,390 --> 00:08:40,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I no longer have any wide-eyed illusions 
about leading a happy life.</font>

157
00:08:42,210 --> 00:08:47,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Uh, it's pretty common 
to feel that way after a breakup,</font>

158
00:08:47,350 --> 00:08:50,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but everybody has the right to be happy...</font>

159
00:08:50,730 --> 00:08:52,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's not what I meant.</font>

160
00:08:52,900 --> 00:08:57,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's just more convenient for me 
if I'm on friendly terms with Arima.</font>

161
00:09:04,390 --> 00:09:06,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'll use everything I can.</i></font>

162
00:09:08,960 --> 00:09:12,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Be it Arima or anyone else.</i></font>

163
00:09:15,530 --> 00:09:18,000
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="22"><font color="#301514">Aqua Hoshino, Son of Former B-Komachi Idol Ai</font></font></b></font>

164
00:09:15,990 --> 00:09:18,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The play is already in motion.</i></font>

165
00:09:18,830 --> 00:09:22,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Everything's going according to plan.</i></font>

166
00:09:26,140 --> 00:09:27,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ai...</font>

167
00:09:27,840 --> 00:09:32,800
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#452519">Hoshino Family Grave</font></font></b></font>

168
00:09:28,390 --> 00:09:32,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I will be the one to make 
your real wish come true.</font>

169
00:09:34,760 --> 00:09:36,220
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="18"><font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#63382a">Hoshino Family Grave</font></font></font></b></font>

170
00:09:35,300 --> 00:09:36,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Look at you,</font>

171
00:09:36,220 --> 00:09:38,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">acting like a star-crossed hero,</font>

172
00:09:38,850 --> 00:09:40,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aqua Hoshino.</font>

173
00:09:41,270 --> 00:09:42,980
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="20"><font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#d8dba4">Youtou Private High School
<font color="#468697">Graduation Ceremony</font></font></font></font></b></font>

174
00:09:44,940 --> 00:09:46,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Senpai!</font>

175
00:09:46,400 --> 00:09:48,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Congratulations on graduating high school!</font>

176
00:09:48,410 --> 00:09:49,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ruby.</font>

177
00:09:49,280 --> 00:09:51,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now you can say that's your 
highest level of education!</font>

178
00:09:52,620 --> 00:09:57,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You keep telling me to go to college, 
but you didn't even apply to any.</font>

179
00:09:57,960 --> 00:10:01,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My life, my choice. I won't need 
any academic qualifications.</font>

180
00:10:01,860 --> 00:10:06,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've made up my mind to live 
and die as an actress in showbiz.</font>

181
00:10:06,820 --> 00:10:11,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll also graduate as an idol after our 
summer concerts and focus on my acting,</font>

182
00:10:11,660 --> 00:10:13,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">using my experience 
with B-Komachi to drive me.</font>

183
00:10:14,910 --> 00:10:16,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know.</font>

184
00:10:19,310 --> 00:10:23,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Graduates are supposed 
to be seen off with a smile.</font>

185
00:10:25,100 --> 00:10:28,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think we'll be able to get 
Frill Shiranui to play Ai.</font>

186
00:10:29,120 --> 00:10:33,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Didn't she only have room in her 
schedule for a supporting role?</font>

187
00:10:33,110 --> 00:10:36,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, but apparently 
one of her projects fell through.</font>

188
00:10:37,410 --> 00:10:40,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A film's main lead is its public face.</font>

189
00:10:40,130 --> 00:10:45,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Frill-chan has the fame to pull it off, 
and an investor asked for her, too.</font>

190
00:10:45,040 --> 00:10:47,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think we should lock her in.</font>

191
00:10:58,640 --> 00:11:00,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You speak cat?</font>

192
00:11:00,370 --> 00:11:01,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whoa, who?!</font>

193
00:11:01,860 --> 00:11:04,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's me, Gotanda. Don't you remember me?</font>

194
00:11:04,310 --> 00:11:07,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, right, the director! It's been ages!</font>

195
00:11:07,910 --> 00:11:11,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think the last time we met 
was your fifteenth birthday.</font>

196
00:11:11,140 --> 00:11:12,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And you gave me 
that video letter from Mom!</font>

197
00:11:12,940 --> 00:11:14,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Takes me back!</font>

198
00:11:13,450 --> 00:11:16,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Genetics truly can be cruel.</i></font>

199
00:11:17,070 --> 00:11:19,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She's grown up to be so beautiful.</i></font>

200
00:11:20,340 --> 00:11:23,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's up? 
Visiting the agency for something?</font>

201
00:11:23,010 --> 00:11:26,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yep. What are you doing out here, though?</font>

202
00:11:26,730 --> 00:11:30,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Uh, there's someone 
I don't want to see in the office.</font>

203
00:11:30,090 --> 00:11:31,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You mean Aqua?</font>

204
00:11:31,590 --> 00:11:34,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I heard you had some kind of falling-out. 
You two still haven't made up?</font>

205
00:11:34,830 --> 00:11:36,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"Still"?</font>

206
00:11:36,880 --> 00:11:39,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">After how he exposed Mom's secret,</font>

207
00:11:39,970 --> 00:11:41,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">how could I ever forgive him?</font>

208
00:11:43,160 --> 00:11:46,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait, didn't Aqua tell you about the DVD?</font>

209
00:11:47,440 --> 00:11:48,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What DVD?</font>

210
00:11:48,740 --> 00:11:49,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Never mind.</font>

211
00:11:50,150 --> 00:11:54,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Is that obsessive brother planning 
to shoulder it all himself?</i></font>

212
00:11:54,450 --> 00:11:56,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>How overprotective can he be?</i></font>

213
00:11:57,040 --> 00:12:01,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Listen, Aqua had his reasons 
for doing what he did.</font>

214
00:12:01,230 --> 00:12:02,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, it doesn't matter.</font>

215
00:12:02,860 --> 00:12:06,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">At this point, I don't really 
care <i>why</i> he did it.</font>

216
00:12:07,210 --> 00:12:10,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It just helped me realize 
you can't trust anyone.</font>

217
00:12:11,340 --> 00:12:14,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because everybody's a big liar.</font>

218
00:12:20,460 --> 00:12:21,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My bad.</font>

219
00:12:22,890 --> 00:12:27,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Come to think of it, Ai was around 
that age when she had kids.</i></font>

220
00:12:29,140 --> 00:12:32,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What set this movie project in motion...</i></font>

221
00:12:32,480 --> 00:12:34,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>was two DVDs.</i></font>

222
00:12:32,480 --> 00:12:34,940
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font face="Comic Sans MS"><font color="#040109">To Onii-chan *</font></font></b></font>

223
00:12:32,480 --> 00:12:34,940
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font face="Comic Sans MS"><font color="#040109">Do not open
till you're 15!</font></font></b></font>

224
00:12:32,480 --> 00:12:34,940
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font face="Comic Sans MS"><font color="#040109">To Ruby <3</font></font></b></font>

225
00:12:32,480 --> 00:12:34,940
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font face="Comic Sans MS"><font color="#040109">Open this
when you're 15</font></font></b></font>

226
00:12:34,940 --> 00:12:35,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Director!</font>

227
00:12:36,070 --> 00:12:37,900
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="28"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><font color="#151818">To Onii-chan *</font></font></font></b></font>

228
00:12:36,070 --> 00:12:37,900
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="28"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><font color="#151818">To Ruby <3</font></font></font></b></font>

229
00:12:36,340 --> 00:12:37,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hold on to these for me!</font>

230
00:12:37,900 --> 00:12:39,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are they?</font>

231
00:12:39,310 --> 00:12:44,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Video letters to the future. 
I've been wanting to try this kinda thing!</font>

232
00:12:44,250 --> 00:12:47,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Give 'em to Aqua and Ruby 
when they turn fifteen.</font>

233
00:12:47,340 --> 00:12:51,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of all the silly ideas... 
Just give them the letters yourself.</font>

234
00:12:51,340 --> 00:12:54,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You know I'd just lose them, right?</font>

235
00:12:54,270 --> 00:12:55,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good point.</font>

236
00:12:55,910 --> 00:12:58,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're not allowed to peek, okay?</font>

237
00:12:58,510 --> 00:13:00,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, yeah.</font>

238
00:13:00,180 --> 00:13:02,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll hand 'em over if I remember.</font>

239
00:13:04,090 --> 00:13:05,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's a promise, okay?</font>

240
00:13:08,770 --> 00:13:11,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I should have given more thought to it.</i></font>

241
00:13:11,510 --> 00:13:14,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Why did she address them 
to Aqua and Ruby at fifteen?</i></font>

242
00:13:14,830 --> 00:13:17,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Why send them separate DVDs?</i></font>

243
00:13:18,190 --> 00:13:23,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Why did Ai leave them with me 
just before she died?</i></font>

244
00:13:23,940 --> 00:13:26,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>When I figured out the answers,</i></font>

245
00:13:26,080 --> 00:13:30,040
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#817579"></font></font></b>Pitch</font>

246
00:13:26,080 --> 00:13:30,040
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="12"><font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#837c7e"></font></font></font></b>Title</font>

247
00:13:26,080 --> 00:13:30,040
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#6d5a62"></font></font></b>The 15-Year Lie</font>

248
00:13:26,080 --> 00:13:30,040
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="12"><font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#5c5658"></font></font></font></b>Details</font>

249
00:13:26,600 --> 00:13:29,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I made up my mind to start this project.</i></font>

250
00:13:30,370 --> 00:13:33,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, who's going to play Ai?</font>

251
00:13:33,190 --> 00:13:37,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Producer Kaburagi 
wants to go with Frill Shiranui.</font>

252
00:13:37,170 --> 00:13:40,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shiranui, huh? She <i>is</i> popular.</font>

253
00:13:40,340 --> 00:13:41,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I have another pick...</font>

254
00:13:43,320 --> 00:13:44,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">for Ai's role.</font>

255
00:13:45,200 --> 00:13:47,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ruby Hoshino is the one 
I want to play her.</font>

256
00:14:03,170 --> 00:14:06,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um, is that what you were looking for?</font>

257
00:14:06,700 --> 00:14:08,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Have you received formal acting training?</font>

258
00:14:08,970 --> 00:14:12,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My agency had me take lessons, 
for what it's worth.</font>

259
00:14:12,830 --> 00:14:17,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I also spend a lot of time around actors, 
so I guess I kinda copied them?</font>

260
00:14:18,140 --> 00:14:20,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see. Thank you.</font>

261
00:14:20,150 --> 00:14:21,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Excuse me.</font>

262
00:14:22,650 --> 00:14:24,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What did I just get screened for?</font>

263
00:14:28,050 --> 00:14:32,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This would've been so much easier 
if she couldn't act at all.</font>

264
00:14:32,780 --> 00:14:36,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why did you have to go and 
complicate things, Gotanda-kun?</font>

265
00:14:36,680 --> 00:14:39,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As you saw, Ruby can act.</font>

266
00:14:39,410 --> 00:14:41,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And we can coach her 
through the finer points as we go.</font>

267
00:14:41,930 --> 00:14:46,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Casting her as Ai will be truer to life 
and give the film more signif—</font>

268
00:14:46,060 --> 00:14:48,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's not the point!</font>

269
00:14:48,210 --> 00:14:51,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The quality and significance of 
the film are secondary concerns!</font>

270
00:14:51,610 --> 00:14:52,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Get it through your skull!</font>

271
00:14:53,880 --> 00:14:55,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure, make faces all you want!</font>

272
00:14:55,650 --> 00:14:58,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But you're a grown man. 
I know you understand this.</font>

273
00:14:58,620 --> 00:15:03,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What matters most is that we repay 
the companies that invested in us.</font>

274
00:15:03,210 --> 00:15:08,720
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="14"><font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#665352">Frill Shiranui</font></font></font></b></font>

275
00:15:03,210 --> 00:15:08,720
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="24"><font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#564440">Ruby</font></font></font></b></font>

276
00:15:03,640 --> 00:15:08,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Casting Frill Shiranui is far likelier 
to put us in the black!</font>

277
00:15:09,020 --> 00:15:11,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As producer, it's my job to ensure 
a commercial success.</font>

278
00:15:11,740 --> 00:15:14,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Frill Shiranui is my top pick, 
and I'm not backing down on that!</font>

279
00:15:15,330 --> 00:15:18,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Producer Kaburagi is totally in the right.</i></font>

280
00:15:18,120 --> 00:15:23,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>You can't talk about the quality of a 
work until it's a commercial success.</i></font>

281
00:15:24,210 --> 00:15:27,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I need this film to be a big hit myself.</i></font>

282
00:15:28,660 --> 00:15:33,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This guy once told me, "This isn't 
a place for art. It's a business,"</i></font>

283
00:15:33,100 --> 00:15:35,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>but I guess that doesn't apply to him?</i></font>

284
00:15:36,640 --> 00:15:40,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Well, he </i>is<i> just a big child who 
happens to be able to make movies.</i></font>

285
00:15:41,070 --> 00:15:42,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Grow up already, man.</i></font>

286
00:15:43,970 --> 00:15:46,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Besides, Ruby's not going to be up for it.</i></font>

287
00:15:47,420 --> 00:15:51,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She can't be ready to tell the truth 
about her mother yet.</i></font>

288
00:15:51,810 --> 00:15:53,520
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="12"><font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#45213d">The 15-Year Lie</font></font></font></b></font>

289
00:15:55,480 --> 00:16:00,440
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}</b><font color="#6a4e5b">I hear they're arguing over the cast
for Director Gotanda's movie lmao

But if they want it to be a hit, they gotta
cast you. Blockbuster name ftw lol</font></font>

290
00:15:56,030 --> 00:16:00,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Industry insiders know an awful lot about 
what happens behind closed doors,</i></font>

291
00:16:00,440 --> 00:16:04,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and many try to use that information 
to network with talent.</i></font>

292
00:16:05,430 --> 00:16:08,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>When I hear talk from people like that,</i></font>

293
00:16:08,220 --> 00:16:11,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I sometimes start to question how 
I should be playing the game myself.</i></font>

294
00:16:11,620 --> 00:16:13,080
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="26"><font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#502726">The 15-Year Lie</font></font></font></b></font>

295
00:16:16,160 --> 00:16:16,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey.</font>

296
00:16:16,950 --> 00:16:17,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hmm?</font>

297
00:16:17,820 --> 00:16:19,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Want to grab some crêpes on the way home?</font>

298
00:16:19,470 --> 00:16:21,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sounds good! Let's ask Minami—</font>

299
00:16:21,460 --> 00:16:22,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ruby.</font>

300
00:16:22,820 --> 00:16:24,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This has to stay between us.</font>

301
00:16:29,040 --> 00:16:33,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wead the scwipt for 
Diwector Gotanda's new film.</font>

302
00:16:35,170 --> 00:16:37,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was originally offered a different role,</font>

303
00:16:37,840 --> 00:16:39,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but my schedule opened up,</font>

304
00:16:39,500 --> 00:16:42,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and now there's talk of me 
playing the lead instead.</font>

305
00:16:42,860 --> 00:16:45,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I hear they're still arguing 
about who to pick, though.</font>

306
00:16:45,790 --> 00:16:47,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh...</font>

307
00:16:47,590 --> 00:16:51,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Oh, so that's why they 
called me in the other day!</font>

308
00:16:51,840 --> 00:16:53,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They didn't tell you?</font>

309
00:16:53,790 --> 00:16:58,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait, so you and me 
are gonna audition for the role?</font>

310
00:16:59,140 --> 00:17:00,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's not going to happen.</font>

311
00:17:01,240 --> 00:17:06,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In Japanese showbiz, big stars 
never have to go through auditions.</font>

312
00:17:06,170 --> 00:17:10,130
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font face="Arial Black">Star Actors</font></b></font>

313
00:17:06,800 --> 00:17:10,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}They only hold them for supporting roles.</font>

314
00:17:06,920 --> 00:17:10,130
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font face="Arial Black"><font color="#f3f8f9">Please join the cast!</font></font></b></font>

315
00:17:07,670 --> 00:17:10,130
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font face="Arial Black"><font color="#f3f8f9">Hmm, I dunno...</font></font></b></font>

316
00:17:10,630 --> 00:17:14,100
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font face="Arial Black"><font color="#faf4f6">Supporting Actors</font></font></b></font>

317
00:17:10,640 --> 00:17:14,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an1}The showrunners can't compare 
people on my level.</font>

318
00:17:10,880 --> 00:17:14,100
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font face="Arial Black"><font color="#f6f9fa">Please cast me!</font></font></b></font>

319
00:17:11,630 --> 00:17:14,100
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font face="Arial Black"><font color="#f6f9fa">Who should I pick...</font></font></b></font>

320
00:17:14,930 --> 00:17:20,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Offers for starring roles and theme songs 
are generally made one at a time.</font>

321
00:17:18,640 --> 00:17:22,980
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font face="Arial Black"><font color="#f3f5f7">Offer</font></font></b></font>

322
00:17:18,640 --> 00:17:22,980
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font face="Arial Black"><font color="#f3f5f7">Offer</font></font></b></font>

323
00:17:18,640 --> 00:17:22,980
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font face="Arial Black"><font color="#444a89">Actor A</font></font></b></font>

324
00:17:18,640 --> 00:17:22,980
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font face="Arial Black"><font color="#424c8c">Actor B</font></font></b></font>

325
00:17:20,000 --> 00:17:22,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Making multiple simultaneous 
offers is seen as unethical.</font>

326
00:17:22,980 --> 00:17:23,980
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font face="Arial Black"><font color="#444a89">Actor</font></font></b></font>

327
00:17:23,430 --> 00:17:27,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Only when the first choice refuses 
do they start negotiating with the second.</font>

328
00:17:24,730 --> 00:17:27,480
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font face="Arial Black"><font color="#444a89">Actor</font></font></b></font>

329
00:17:24,730 --> 00:17:27,480
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font face="Arial Black"><font color="#444a89">Actor B</font></font></b></font>

330
00:17:25,980 --> 00:17:27,480
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font face="Arial Black"><font color="#444a89">Actor C</font></font></b></font>

331
00:17:27,820 --> 00:17:33,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Actors who get lots of lead role offers 
get to pick and choose.</font>

332
00:17:33,690 --> 00:17:36,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In other words, I'm interviewing <i>them</i>.</font>

333
00:17:37,050 --> 00:17:40,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Making big stars audition 
is utterly disrespectful!</font>

334
00:17:41,370 --> 00:17:44,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">At least, that's the view 
of the producers and agents.</font>

335
00:17:45,370 --> 00:17:47,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's not like we ourselves 
really see it that way, though.</font>

336
00:17:47,830 --> 00:17:52,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'd prefer to be chosen on merit, 
not because of fame or connections.</font>

337
00:17:52,510 --> 00:17:55,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Top stars have their own stuff 
to worry about, huh?</font>

338
00:17:55,350 --> 00:17:58,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yep. I agonize over it, sometimes 
to the point of depression.</font>

339
00:17:59,680 --> 00:18:02,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's our job to make quality films,</font>

340
00:18:03,270 --> 00:18:07,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and yet there are times when 
the quality drops because of us.</font>

341
00:18:07,970 --> 00:18:10,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Actors should be chosen on merit.</font>

342
00:18:10,750 --> 00:18:12,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't you agree?</font>

343
00:18:15,630 --> 00:18:16,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I do.</font>

344
00:18:16,690 --> 00:18:17,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right?</font>

345
00:18:17,980 --> 00:18:19,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's do just that, then.</font>

346
00:18:19,260 --> 00:18:19,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

347
00:18:20,340 --> 00:18:24,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But didn't you say the showrunners 
can't compare us—</font>

348
00:18:24,490 --> 00:18:27,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The showrunners can't.</font>

349
00:18:27,050 --> 00:18:29,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But what if we did it ourselves?</font>

350
00:18:30,270 --> 00:18:33,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's have a showdown, Ruby. 
Whoever loses has to turn down the offer.</font>

351
00:18:33,950 --> 00:18:37,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That way, the winner 
will get the role by default.</font>

352
00:18:37,650 --> 00:18:38,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We can call it...</font>

353
00:18:39,150 --> 00:18:40,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">a private audition.</font>

354
00:18:42,430 --> 00:18:44,140
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font face="Comic Sans MS"><font color="#f9f9f9">North Exit Shopping Arcade
Hula Dance Club
Private Audition
Sunflower R&R
Yasuoka</font></font></b></font>

355
00:18:43,010 --> 00:18:44,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow.</font>

356
00:18:44,420 --> 00:18:46,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I didn't know you could 
rent out a place like this.</font>

357
00:18:47,050 --> 00:18:51,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Broke theater groups and underground 
idols often use them for lessons.</font>

358
00:18:51,710 --> 00:18:56,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Community centers like this 
have nonsensically cheap rental fees.</font>

359
00:18:56,230 --> 00:18:57,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh? How much?</font>

360
00:18:57,850 --> 00:18:59,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Two hundred yen for two hours.</font>

361
00:18:59,380 --> 00:19:00,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

362
00:19:00,200 --> 00:19:01,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Two hundred yen for two hours!</font>

363
00:19:01,740 --> 00:19:03,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's nonsensically cheap!</font>

364
00:19:03,910 --> 00:19:08,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's a government facility built using 
the citizens' blood, sweat, and taxes.</font>

365
00:19:08,700 --> 00:19:11,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's be grateful for the chance 
to squeeze it for all it's worth.</font>

366
00:19:11,340 --> 00:19:14,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The silent wrath of the highest 
tax bracket! Ooh, scary!</font>

367
00:19:15,260 --> 00:19:18,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, what are we doing for this audition?</font>

368
00:19:18,630 --> 00:19:19,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Could it be...</font>

369
00:19:20,100 --> 00:19:22,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huff-puff, huff-puff!</font>

370
00:19:22,000 --> 00:19:23,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Eep!</font>

371
00:19:23,330 --> 00:19:25,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tremble-tremble, panic-panic!</font>

372
00:19:25,220 --> 00:19:26,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Eek!</font>

373
00:19:26,730 --> 00:19:28,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Something like that?</font>

374
00:19:28,240 --> 00:19:30,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Relax. We won't be putting 
our lives on the line.</font>

375
00:19:32,400 --> 00:19:33,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry to keep you waiting.</font>

376
00:19:37,530 --> 00:19:39,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Akane-chan.</font>

377
00:19:39,170 --> 00:19:41,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good. Now we have all of 
the lead role candidates here.</font>

378
00:19:43,120 --> 00:19:44,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Long time no see, Ruby-chan.</font>

379
00:19:44,940 --> 00:19:46,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">U-Uh...</font>

380
00:19:46,210 --> 00:19:47,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah...</font>

381
00:19:51,170 --> 00:19:53,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Awkward!</i></font>

382
00:19:52,920 --> 00:19:56,130
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="8"><font color="#f6ff19">Hooked Up On Love for Real</font></font></b></font>

383
00:19:52,920 --> 00:19:56,130
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="16"><font color="#d52149">Popular Couple <font color="#fdff18">Splits</font></font></font></b></font>

384
00:19:52,920 --> 00:19:56,130
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="16"><font color="#d52149">Popular Couple <font color="#fdff18">Splits</font></font></font></b></font>

385
00:19:52,920 --> 00:19:56,130
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="10">Aqua Hoshino</font></b></font>

386
00:19:52,920 --> 00:19:56,130
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="10">Akane Kurokawa</font></b></font>

387
00:19:53,500 --> 00:19:56,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>They just announced
their breakup and everything!</i></font>

388
00:19:56,790 --> 00:19:59,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But I did call her my big sis once.</i></font>

389
00:19:59,820 --> 00:20:01,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I gotta play it cool!</i></font>

390
00:20:01,600 --> 00:20:03,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How's Aqua-kun? Is he doing okay?</font>

391
00:20:03,870 --> 00:20:04,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-Yeah...</font>

392
00:20:05,300 --> 00:20:06,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Eek!</i></font>

393
00:20:07,130 --> 00:20:10,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shiranui-san, 
what are you playing at here?</font>

394
00:20:10,390 --> 00:20:11,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you mean?</font>

395
00:20:11,480 --> 00:20:16,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're the top choices for the lead role 
in Director Gotanda's new film, right?</font>

396
00:20:16,790 --> 00:20:19,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you'd let things play out, 
you would've gotten the offer first.</font>

397
00:20:19,860 --> 00:20:25,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But here you are, making a mess of things. 
So what are you playing at?</font>

398
00:20:25,080 --> 00:20:26,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nothing at all.</font>

399
00:20:26,700 --> 00:20:27,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Liar.</font>

400
00:20:30,750 --> 00:20:33,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not very trusting, are you, Kurokawa-san?</font>

401
00:20:36,500 --> 00:20:39,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fine. I do have a goal of sorts.</font>

402
00:20:39,420 --> 00:20:41,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is it?</font>

403
00:20:41,050 --> 00:20:41,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's a secret.</font>

404
00:20:42,750 --> 00:20:45,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That said, the reason 
I proposed this private audition</font>

405
00:20:46,370 --> 00:20:50,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">is ninety percent because I want 
to feel good about doing my job.</font>

406
00:20:51,470 --> 00:20:56,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want to go into it thinking, 
"I really was the best fit for this role."</font>

407
00:20:56,820 --> 00:21:00,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not my problem. This is the 
first day off I've had in ages.</font>

408
00:21:00,580 --> 00:21:02,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If that's all this is, I'm out of here.</font>

409
00:21:02,300 --> 00:21:04,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll be acting opposite Aqua-san.</font>

410
00:21:04,780 --> 00:21:06,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aqua?</font>

411
00:21:07,550 --> 00:21:09,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You say this is an audition.</font>

412
00:21:09,780 --> 00:21:11,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who's judging it?</font>

413
00:21:11,770 --> 00:21:15,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's between us. We'll decide the winner.</font>

414
00:21:16,240 --> 00:21:17,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's the litmus test?</font>

415
00:21:17,870 --> 00:21:20,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why don't we just play the part?</font>

416
00:21:20,470 --> 00:21:24,430
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#3a1a3a">The 15-Year Lie</font></font></b></font>

417
00:21:20,910 --> 00:21:24,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I haven't gotten the script. 
I don't know what the part even is.</font>

418
00:21:24,430 --> 00:21:26,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Me neither.</font>

419
00:21:26,260 --> 00:21:27,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, right.</font>

420
00:21:27,800 --> 00:21:32,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't really show the script to people 
who haven't gotten an offer yet...</font>

421
00:21:32,790 --> 00:21:37,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hmm... In that case, 
how about I pick a theme,</font>

422
00:21:37,360 --> 00:21:40,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and we each improvise a scene on that?</font>

423
00:21:40,420 --> 00:21:41,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fine by me.</font>

424
00:21:41,520 --> 00:21:42,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yep.</font>

425
00:21:42,600 --> 00:21:44,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, let's go with that.</font>

426
00:21:44,050 --> 00:21:45,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The theme is...</font>

427
00:21:45,070 --> 00:21:46,280
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font face="Times New Roman"><font size="40"><font color="#1d1d1f">Lie</font></font></font></b></font>

428
00:21:46,660 --> 00:21:47,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"Liar."</font>

429
00:21:50,420 --> 00:21:54,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll go first. Use the time 
to think about what you'll do.</font>

430
00:21:56,120 --> 00:21:58,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">First up, here is Frill Shiranui,</font>

431
00:21:58,560 --> 00:21:59,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">with "Liar."</font>

432
00:22:02,470 --> 00:22:05,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Awoo!</font>

433
00:22:06,430 --> 00:22:08,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wolf!</font>

434
00:22:08,500 --> 00:22:10,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wolf!</font>

435
00:22:10,750 --> 00:22:13,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wolf!</font>

436
00:22:14,250 --> 00:22:18,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tch, not a damn soul believes me anymore.</font>

437
00:22:18,900 --> 00:22:21,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wish they'd give me attention.</font>

438
00:22:22,090 --> 00:22:23,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm so lonely...</font>

439
00:22:29,290 --> 00:22:31,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What the hell should I do?</font>

440
00:22:34,980 --> 00:22:39,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know! Maybe they'll give me 
attention if I tell the truth?</font>

441
00:22:40,590 --> 00:22:43,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No wolf!</font>

442
00:22:43,620 --> 00:22:47,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And then men from all over the village 
showed up with their hunting rifles</font>

443
00:22:47,920 --> 00:22:52,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and raked the boy 
who cried wolf over the coals.</font>

444
00:22:52,730 --> 00:22:54,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fin.</font>

445
00:22:55,040 --> 00:22:55,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

446
00:22:55,900 --> 00:22:56,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A skit?</font>

447
00:22:57,250 --> 00:23:00,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oops, my comedian side shone through.</font>

448
00:23:00,420 --> 00:23:04,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You two don't need punchlines, okay? 
Do whatever you like.</font>

449
00:23:04,740 --> 00:23:08,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So yeah, I can act a bit.</font>

450
00:23:08,570 --> 00:23:10,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not as much as Kurokawa-san, of course.</font>

451
00:23:11,300 --> 00:23:14,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I do have a sort of appeal 
that only I can bring to a role,</font>

452
00:23:14,660 --> 00:23:17,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so I'd like you to take that into account.</font>

453
00:23:17,420 --> 00:23:21,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Being good at acting isn't the only 
thing that makes a good actor.</i></font>

454
00:23:21,460 --> 00:23:26,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She has an air about her that draws 
the eyes of one and all to herself.</i></font>

455
00:23:26,910 --> 00:23:29,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That's a powerful asset for any actor.</i></font>

456
00:23:29,800 --> 00:23:32,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, your turn next, Ruby.</font>

457
00:23:33,320 --> 00:23:37,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>If this were any other audition, 
Ruby-chan wouldn't stand a chance.</i></font>

458
00:23:37,820 --> 00:23:40,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>So there must be a reason 
she's a part of this,</i></font>

459
00:23:41,110 --> 00:23:43,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and I'm betting it has to do 
with this role—this movie.</i></font>

460
00:23:44,510 --> 00:23:45,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Say, Ruby.</font>

461
00:23:45,900 --> 00:23:49,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What does lying mean to you?</font>

462
00:23:56,620 --> 00:24:00,000
<font face="Times New Roman" size="32" color="#0a0a0a"><b>{\an8}Episode 33










Greed and Passion</b></font>

463
